<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.2">
<l>peyvaḷaik kaikaḷaik kūppip pirāṉkiṭak kuṅkaṭa leṉṉuñ</l>
<l>ceyyatōr ñāyiṟṟaik kāṭṭic cirītaraṉ mūrttiyī teṉṉu</l>
<l>naiyuṅkaṇ ṇīrmalka niṉṟu nāraṇa ṉeṉṉu maṉṉēyeṉ</l>
<l>ṟeyva vuruvil ciṟumāṉ ceykiṉṟa toṉṟaṟi yēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Folding [her] hands with bangles to wear she says “[this is] the ocean on which the lord lies”,</l>
<l>pointing at a red sun she says “this [is] the form of the bearer of Śrī”,</l>
<l>standing while crushing tears rise she indeed says “Nāraṇaṉ”.</l>
<l>What my little doe of divine shape  does I do not understand at all.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
